data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to your oceanfront oasis, where every wave tells a story, and every sunrise is a masterpiece. This stunning condo, perched across from the water's edge, is a testament to luxury living, offering an unparalleled blend of style, comfort, and breathtaking ocean views.  As you step inside, you are greeted by an atmosphere of sophistication. The entire space has undergone a meticulous renovation, leaving no detail untouched. The open-concept design seamlessly integrates the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a fluid and inviting environment. High-end finishes and top-of-the-line materials are used throughout, enhancing the overall aesthetic and quality of the residence.  The living room is a showcase of modern elegance, featuring windows that frame the panoramic ocean views. Imagine relaxing on your sofa, surrounded by the gentle sound of waves and the warm glow of natural light, creating the perfect ambiance for intimate gatherings or quiet moments of reflection.  The kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting state-of-the-art appliances, custom cabinetry, and sleek countertops. Whether you're preparing a casual breakfast or hosting a gourmet dinner party, this kitchen is both functional and visually stunning. It's a space where culinary creativity meets the art of entertaining.  The master bedroom is a sanctuary of tranquility, overlooking the endless expanse of the ocean. Wake up to the soothing sound of waves, witness the sunrise – a daily spectacle that becomes a cherished ritual.   Every inch of this turn-key condo has been thoughtfully curated to provide an unexpected level of luxury. The interior exudes a sense of opulence that complements the natural beauty just beyond your windows. This oceanfront haven goes beyond the expected – it invites you to experience a lifestyle of indulgence, where the sea becomes an integral part of your daily existence. Welcome home to a place where the extraordinary is the norm, and each day unfolds against the backdrop of an endless horizon.
